column5: Another great day on the Grand ..lots of people with fish today ..and also lots with no fish ..brisk day out there today wind chill was cold …looks like things are shapen up good for the Tourney Next Weekend ..lets hope fishing keeps up ..ice thickness is 6 to 7” ..ive have been running my Skidoo on the river and seen some atv’s out today …just be carefull and don’t even try to go down river towards Vic Powells Ship Yard….as allways play safe ….Fishmaster Todays big fish ...& lots of other hogs released today .. Fishlips staying  on fish for the Derby next weekend ..   Fishfarmer with a ncie Walleye nice seeing  you today …
Killer season on the Grand so far! Startin' to remind me of BOQ.
those are some big fish!  Thanks for the report!  Cheers!
....FishFarmer caught something, I don't believe it! Guess I'll try and get down there this afternoon.
If you go, stay out of my lucky hole.   You can fish in Glens hole, he came off with an empty pail Good luck Chris catch the BIG ONE
Beauty fish!  Still waiting for the spring thaw though....LOL.
will be out there monday morning easton,,,,why don't ya try and make it out? And as for how i'm making out,,,,,hmmm it's the experiance that counts!!!
I have $10.00's to either you or easton if you are interested in having Zachary Join you for fishing monday.  Fish in the hut for him is my bet!
nice fish, congrats, was out Sat. no fish but nice day. would like to return Monday. How's the ice holding up, much rain up their.  thanks Noweyton
looks like the Grand is going good, too bad niagara was too muddy again for last friday.. hopefully soon!
